{"tid":1936752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成班狗鳩企除咗將個場變成死城同提醒大家721絕對係警黑合作之外，仲有咩作用？","createTime":"2020-03-21T12:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T12:35:16.000Z","uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcecca246b69129ac6f9ff926edceeefb38b7b9","tid":1936752,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q5826fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5826fs.jpg&h=ff84ee0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1945 #銅鑼灣 #銅鑼灣站<br />\n銅鑼灣站內有市民大叫「我只係支持正義嘅人，警察係垃圾」，當有警察聽到支持正義的人並回答「咁咪支持我哋」。<br />\n#蘋果<br />\n小編O：相當厚顏無恥呀吓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hrc3QHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrc3QHs.jpg&h=02f1dd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1947 #銅鑼灣 #銅鑼灣站<br />\n有市民大叫「警察亂咁打人」，一名便衣警察回應「有病就返屋企啦」。<br />\n#蘋果<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有人早前在G出口張貼「藍絲」連儂牆，貼上多張指摘示威者是「暴徒」的文宣，警員則有別過去做法，選擇視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n有市民不齒港鐵和警方派駐多人駐守站內，<span style=\"color: red;\">批評：「7.21又唔見你哋咁多人？」、「企哂喺度啦咩而家？」</span><br />\n毋忘7.21恐襲 元朗巴士站市民自發清藍絲文宣 警到場驅趕<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33DidcZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33DidcZ&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=7f3f8140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33DidcZ</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"87e5a58e34c5815adef049b7deec59d5bc6a5938","tid":1936752,"uid":118385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e645eee3b4d4f41e40ec2e19447e05a4e31e901","tid":1936752,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"個個月整多幾個back up 地點等班過街老鼠岀嚟宵禁和你shop啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去老蘭soho"},{"pid":"25b2c6936505d8ddaf21261dc8d11b2eb08f5cf4","tid":1936752,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"